Class MetaTagNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.common.SourceLocation

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDecoration, IMetaInfo, ISourceLocation, IASNode, IMetaTagNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseDefinitionMetaTagNode, BasicMetaTagNode, DefaultPropertyTagNode, EventTriggerTagNode, InspectableTagNode, MultiValueMetaTagNode, ResourceBundleTagNode, TypedTagNode

    public abstract class MetaTagNode
extends TreeNode
implements IMetaTagNode
    MetaAttributeNode is a generic node holding info for one metadata attribute. The name of the attribute is the meta name ("Inspectable", "Bindable", "Style", etc.) (not the name of any "name" attribute within the tag)
